  <channel>
    <title>Refugees contributor: Sonia Narang</title>
    <description>Sonia Narang is a multimedia journalist who covers global health, education, culture, and more. She primarily reports on the lives of women and girls, and the challenges they face around the world. Sonia’s radio and visual work also airs on PRI’s The World, and her assignments have taken her across India, Nepal, Pakistan, Indonesia, the Philippines, Japan, and the US. Follow her on Twitter and Instagram @sonianarang.
</description>
